      "writtenOn": "2021-07-16T18:26:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The subtly of this problem is in the ordering of update, and buildProgram. Since update will be called by update, and the values are stored at that time, then those values must persist through the call to buildProgram. Therefore, buildProgram must take a different set of uniforms to not harm the data set by update.",
      "parentUuid": "55eee740_0065e2cb",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 416,
        "startChar": 24,
        "endLine": 416,
        "endChar": 33
      },
